<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Post-Session Capture Template</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #FDFBF7;
            padding: 2rem;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2D2D2D;
        }
        .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h1 {
            font-family: Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle { color: #4A6274; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        h2 {
            font-family: Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .prompt {
            background: #F5F0E8;
            border: 1px solid #E8E4DC;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #4A6274;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100px;
            border: 1px solid #E8E4DC;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            resize: vertical;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        textarea:focus { outline: 2px solid #DEBA85; border-color: #DEBA85; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Post-Session Capture</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Fill this out immediately after the session — while it's fresh.</p>

        <h2>1. What surprised you about the room?</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Energy level, engagement patterns, who was ahead/behind your expectations</div>
        <textarea placeholder="What surprised you..."></textarea>

        <h2>2. Who was most engaged? What were they working on?</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Names, what they built, what lit them up</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Most engaged attendees..."></textarea>

        <h2>3. Who was hesitant? What might help?</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Names, what they struggled with, what kind of follow-up might unlock them</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Hesitant attendees..."></textarea>

        <h2>4. Boundary questions that came up</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Any gray areas, edge cases, "what about..." questions about the traffic light card</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Boundary questions..."></textarea>

        <h2>5. Use cases that emerged</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Specific tasks people wanted to use AI for — these feed the follow-up session and expanded prompt library</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Use cases..."></textarea>

        <h2>6. What to do differently next time</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Timing, pacing, what to add/cut, what worked, what fell flat</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Next time..."></textarea>

        <h2>7. Follow-up actions</h2>
        <div class="prompt">Who needs what? Additional access, training, resources, 1:1 time?</div>
        <textarea placeholder="Follow-up actions..."></textarea>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
